{"tid":409470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港青冇用?】 90後兄弟發跡  取英國籍 同為劍橋生 任企業高管","createTime":"2017-09-22T05:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T06:28:46.000Z","uid":82646,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce0f09519a652a3d74dea02665aef3a353cfe57","tid":409470,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:26:44.000Z","msg":"洋名為Jeremy的林節思現年26歲，據他在社交平台Linkedin的資料顯示，2005至2010年間，他在英國切特豪斯公學讀書，其後入讀劍橋大學純數系。2013年畢業後，2013年至2014年間，曾在周大福慈善基金做項目經理；2015年至2016年，則在內地公司啟明創投基金任職；去年4月起，到北京加入內地手機公司小米，出任營運經理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相比兄長，現年23歲的 Josh林約希，目前他仍在英國留學，於劍橋大學修讀數學，過去曾兩度在國際數學奧林匹克比賽中奪獎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1339371_1_L_20170701091302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1339371_1_L_20170701091302.jpg&h=774b4055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJeremy 向傳媒分享"},{"pid":"e17f798c8fed3f9e8863bda0148bbad0fb6af9b1","tid":409470,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:27:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d53c9fa36bb12d95922b142e11c52cdd3735e24a","tid":409470,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼紅牙?"},{"pid":"e40a7b69b71a35cbaaa96972111096f6e968553f","tid":409470,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:31:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼紅牙?</blockquote><br />\n牙你老母"},{"pid":"7809ee9d315a3231a35a15395a91dcade7fc4ae5","tid":409470,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼紅牙?</blockquote><br />\n連登仔實屌人做小米"},{"pid":"e9c2bd